{"config":{"lang":["en"],"separator":"[\\s\\-]+","pipeline":["stopWordFilter"],"fields":{"title":{"boost":1000.0},"text":{"boost":1.0},"tags":{"boost":1000000.0}}},"docs":[{"location":"","title":"Boilerplate 2026","text":"<p>Welcome to the official documentation.</p>"},{"location":"#features","title":"Features","text":"<ul> <li>Laravel 11</li> <li>Docker</li> <li>Nginx</li> <li>PHP 8.3</li> <li>MariaDB</li> <li>Filament v3</li> <li>HTTPS Local Domain</li> <li>GitHub Automation</li> <li>Custom CLI Commands</li> <li>Auto Repository Creation</li> </ul>"},{"location":"#documentation","title":"Documentation","text":"<ul> <li>Installation</li> <li>Commands</li> <li>Docker</li> <li>GitHub Integration</li> <li>FAQ</li> </ul>"},{"location":"#update","title":"Update","text":"<p>Testing auto deployment.</p> <pre><code>Semoga Bermanfaat dan Happy Coding \u2764\ufe0f\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"commands/","title":"\u26a1 Commands","text":""},{"location":"commands/#dcu","title":"dcu","text":"<pre><code>dcu\n</code></pre> <p>Start Docker.</p>"},{"location":"commands/#dcd","title":"dcd","text":"<pre><code>dcd\n</code></pre> <p>Stop Docker.</p>"},{"location":"commands/#dcm","title":"dcm","text":"<pre><code>dcm User\n</code></pre> <p>Generate:</p> <ul> <li>Model</li> <li>Migration</li> <li>Seeder</li> <li>Controller</li> <li>Filament Resource</li> </ul>"},{"location":"commands/#dcr","title":"dcr","text":"<p>Remove generated files.</p>"},{"location":"commands/#dcp","title":"dcp","text":"<pre><code>dcp \"update user model\"\n</code></pre> <p>Automatically:</p> <ul> <li>git add</li> <li>git commit</li> <li>git pull --rebase</li> <li>git push</li> </ul>"},{"location":"commands/#dci","title":"dci","text":"<p>Initialize project.</p>"},{"location":"docker/","title":"\ud83d\udc33 Docker","text":"<p>Services</p> Service Port Nginx 80 / 443 PHP Internal MariaDB 13306 <p>Useful Commands</p> <pre><code>docker compose ps\ndocker compose logs -f\ndocker compose down\ndocker compose build\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"faq/","title":"\u2753 FAQ","text":""},{"location":"faq/#docker-wont-start","title":"Docker won't start","text":"<pre><code>docker compose logs\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"faq/#https-not-working","title":"HTTPS not working","text":"<p>Run</p> <pre><code>mkcert -install\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"faq/#github-push-failed","title":"GitHub push failed","text":"<p>Check</p> <ul> <li>PAT Token</li> <li>Internet</li> <li>Repository Permission</li> </ul>"},{"location":"faq/#project-not-opening","title":"Project not opening","text":"<p>Restart WSL</p> <pre><code>wsl --shutdown\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"github/","title":"\u2601 GitHub","text":"<p>Boilerplate can automatically</p> <ul> <li>Create Repository</li> <li>Push Initial Commit</li> <li>Generate README</li> <li>Configure Git</li> </ul> <p>Required</p> <pre><code>.github-user\n.github-token\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"installation/","title":"\ud83d\udce6 Installation","text":""},{"location":"installation/#clone","title":"Clone","text":"<pre><code>git clone https://github.com/illhammf/boilerplate.git\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"installation/#requirements","title":"Requirements","text":"<ul> <li>WSL Ubuntu</li> <li>Docker Desktop</li> <li>mkcert</li> <li>Git</li> <li>jq</li> </ul>"},{"location":"installation/#run","title":"Run","text":"<pre><code>./start.sh myproject\n</code></pre> <p>Done \ud83c\udf89</p>"}]}